INSERT INTO system (
                symbol,
                constellation,
                population_disabled,
                sector_symbol,
                system_type,
                x,
                y
            )
            SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
                $1::character varying[],
                $2::character varying[],
                $3::boolean[],
                $4::character varying[],
                $5::system_type[],
                $6::integer[],
                $7::integer[]
            )
            ON CONFLICT (symbol) DO UPDATE
            SET sector_symbol = EXCLUDED.sector_symbol,
                constellation = EXCLUDED.constellation,
                population_disabled = EXCLUDED.population_disabled,
                system_type = EXCLUDED.system_type,
                x = EXCLUDED.x,
                y = EXCLUDED.y
